.TH "%PACKAGE%" 1 \
    "%DATE%" \
    "%PACKAGE_NAME% Version %PACKAGE_VERSION%"
.
.
.SH NAME
%PACKAGE% \- simple space status tray icon
.
.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.
.SY %PACKAGE%
.OP \-r n
.OP \-p port
.OP \-t n
.OP \-y n
.OP \-c color
.OP \-b color
.OP \-f font
.RI [ destination ]
.IR
.YS
.
.
.SH DESCRIPTION
.
\*(SP is a simple program for displaying the current
status of a space API.
.
.
.SH OPTIONS
.
.IP "\fB-r\fR \fIn"
Query the space API every
.I n
minutes ( default
.I 5
minutes).
.IP "\fB-p\fR \fIport"
Query the space API on this port ( default
.I 80
).
.IP "\fB-t\fR \fIn"
Display the notification and/or bubble
.I n
seconds ( default
.I 3
seconds).
.IP "\fB-y\fR \fIn"
Display the tooltip
.I n
pixel below/above the tray icon (Position depends on
the position of your traybar) ( default
.I 65
pixel).
.IP "\fB-c\fR \fIcolor"
Set the tooltip foreground color to
.I color
(given in rgb hex format) ( default
.I ffffff
).
.IP "\fB-b\fR \fIcolor"
Set the tooltip background color to
.I color
(given in rgb hex format) ( default
.I 000000
).
.IP "\fB-f\fR \fIfont"
Set the tooltip font to
.I font.
.
.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.
\*(SP will return a non-null exit code if an error occurred.
.
.
.SH FILES
.
.TP
.B %pkgdatadir%/{open,closed,pending}.xpm
Icons used for different tray states.
.
.
